OL,3,CIslanders conquer 24-hour charity
OL,4,Cgaming marathon in Guernsey
OL,6,FJames told ITV News: "The first 12
OL,7,Fhours are always quite electric, I
OL,8,Flike to say. There's always an
OL,9,Fexcellent atmosphere, everyone's
OL,10,Fperky, everyone's good to go.
OL,12,F"It gets to midnight, the sun goes
OL,13,Fdown, every starts to slow down there
OL,14,Fbut the biggest challenge is always
OL,15,Fthe 4am to 5am slot because that's
OL,16,Fwhen no-one's smiling anymore and it's
OL,17,Fjust faces looking at screens in front
OL,18,Fof them and it's a very sombre
OL,19,Fatmosphere!"
