OL,3,CIslanders conquer 24-hour charity
OL,4,Cgaming marathon in Guernsey
OL,6,FThe whole event was live-streamed so
OL,7,Fpeople around the world could cheer on
OL,8,Ftheir friends and donate.
OL,10,FKyle Gallie, one of the seasoned
OL,11,Fgamers, even got dressed up for the
OL,12,Fchallenge.JHe told ITV News: "I
OL,13,Fusually like to dress for the
OL,14,Foccasion. I've dressed as Ash for
OL,15,FPokemon stadium tournaments.
OL,17,F"I've got dressed as Mario for a Mario
OL,18,FKart tournament. So, today, for
OL,19,FFootball Manager, I thought I'd dress
OL,20,Fas a manager ready for his cup final!"
